Title: 153: Tips to Improve your Memory
Description:
In this episode of the SuperDataScience Podcast, I chat with the founder of Magnetic Memory Method, Anthony Metivier. You will hear about the 7 magnetic modes to easily memorize stuff, learn how to find your own memory palace and navigate through it, and know how to use memory techniques in your day-to-day life.


If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at www.superdatascience.com/153
